public class RolloverNotification extends AbstractContractNotification
A loan servicing notification designed to communicate the combination of business events associated with a rollover transaction.

Java class for RolloverNotification complex type.

    • getBaseRateSetOrBorrowingOrCommitmentAdjustment

      public List<LoanEvent> getBaseRateSetOrBorrowingOrCommitmentAdjustment()
      Gets the value of the baseRateSetOrBorrowingOrCommitmentAdjustment property.

      This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the Jakarta XML Binding object. This is why there is not a set method for the baseRateSetOrBorrowingOrCommitmentAdjustment property.

      For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

          getBaseRateSetOrBorrowingOrCommitmentAdjustment().add(newItem);

      Objects of the following type(s) are allowed in the list LoanContractBaseRateSet Borrowing CommitmentAdjustment InterestCapitalization InterestPayment Repayment
